If	other	than	Allah,	there	were	Gods	*	in	the	heavens	and	the	earth,	they	would	be	destroyed;	
therefore	Purity	is	to	Allah,	Owner	of	the	Throne,	from	the	matters	that	they	fabricate.	(*	Which	
is	not	possible.	**	The	heavens	and	the	earth.)

And	 indeed	 We	 gave	 Moosa	 and	 Haroon	
the	Judgement	*	and	a	light	and	an	advice	
for	the	pious.	(*	The	Holy	Book	Taurat.)
